S.FORM: = Paudadan{大德﹙巴烏拉藍﹚部落} = Gaga mniq Hwareyseyn Sincungsyang ka alang Paudadan. 254 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 727 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 72% niqan 526 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 28% niqan 201 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Amis48%, Sakizaya 1%, Bunun 4%, Tayal 4%, Truku 12%, Kebalan 1%, ni rahuq na o 3%.

= Paodadan{大德﹙巴烏拉藍﹚部落} = Gaga mniq Hwareyseyn Sincongsyang ka alang Paodadan. 254 sapah ka kneego na sapah, 727 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnposo seejiq o mangal 72% niqan 526 hiyi sp, rahoq na oxay tnposo seejiq o mangal 28% niqan 201 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Amis48%, Sakizaya 1%, Bonon 4%, Tayal 4%, Troko 12%, Kebalan 1%, ni rahoq na o 3%.
